review 5:
This hotel is not a 3* but the attention to making our stay comfortable was amazing. The staff could not do enough for us including cooking little Balinese treats and lovely evening meals. Breakfast was good too. Surrounded by beautiful flora and rice plantation it is a quiet peaceful and relaxing environment. Although off the tourist radar there is always a wonderful taxi and tour guide available to take you where ever you want to go at a very reasonable price.
We would certainly come back.
